<section class="text-flow">

  <h2>Structured care instead of occasional checks</h2>

  <p>
    Property care requires consistency. Irregular visits without a defined structure do not provide a reliable understanding of the property's condition. What matters is a system that is applied continuously.
  </p>

  <h3>Core principles</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>defined inspection intervals</li>
    <li>consistent inspection routines</li>
    <li>clear documentation of observations</li>
    <li>reliable reporting</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    This creates a continuous overview, making changes visible at an early stage.
  </p>

</section>

