<section class="text-flow">

  <h2>Inspection areas in detail</h2>

  <h3>Interior</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>general condition of rooms and fittings</li>
    <li>signs of humidity or changes</li>
    <li>visible irregularities in daily condition</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Exterior</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>access points, terraces and outdoor areas</li>
    <li>exposure to weather and surroundings</li>
    <li>overall exterior appearance</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Technical condition</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>visible deviations in essential systems</li>
    <li>indications of required measures</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    Combining these areas allows for a complete and accurate assessment of the current condition.
  </p>

</section>

