<section class="text-flow">

  <h2>Storm check as an additional control layer</h2>

  <p>
    After periods of intense weather, an additional inspection is essential to identify potential impacts in a structured way.
  </p>

  <h3>Focus areas</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>outdoor and exposed areas</li>
    <li>windows, openings and structural exposure</li>
    <li>signs of water ingress</li>
    <li>changes in overall condition</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    The storm check complements regular inspections and adds a specific focus on external influences.
  </p>

